    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The sending or bringing back of persons to their country of citizenship or of legal or cultural property to its country, land, or culture of origin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
